name: ALUMINUM TEARS
description: BACK IN 2015 I WAS HELPING WITH DISASTER RELIEF IN CALIFORNIA AFTER THE WILDFIRES, WITH AN ORGANIZATION THAT ONLY USES TYPEWRITERS. WITH THEM MY 10 FINGER TYPE COURSE IN MIDDLE SCHOOL FINALLY PAID OFF. IT WAS CRAZY TO SEE ALL THE LIQUIFIED THEN SOLIDIFIED ALUMINUM ALL OVER THE PLACE.
